<!DOCTYPE html>
<% var patientName; %>
<% var patientAge; %>
<% var patientEmail; %>
<% var patientGender; %>
<% var patientProfilePic; %>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9caaa1478d.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://media.flaticon.com/dist/min/img/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
    <title>HelTH+</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-primary navbar-light sticky-top">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="index" class="navbar-brand"><img src="img/logo.png"></a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#navbarCollapse"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div id="navbarCollapse" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a href="index" class="nav-link">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a href="vaccination" class="nav-link">Vaccination</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a href="appointment" class="nav-link">Appointments</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a href="login" class="nav-link active">Profile</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a href="contact" class="nav-link">Contact Us</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="main-body py-4">
        <div class="row gutters-sm">
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center text-center">
                  <img
                    src= <%= patientProfilePic %>
                    alt="Admin"
                    class="rounded-circle"
                    width="150"
                  />
                  <div class="mt-3">
                    <h4><%= patientName %></h4>
                  </div>
                  <form method="GET" action="/login">
                    <button class="btn btn-danger mx-auto" type="submit">Logout</button>
                  </form>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card mb-3">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-3">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Age</h6>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-9 text-secondary"><%= patientAge %></div>
                </div>
                <hr />
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-3">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Gender</h6>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-9 text-secondary"><%= patientGender %></div>
                </div>
                <hr />
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-3">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Email</h6>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-9 text-secondary"><%= patientEmail %></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="card-header">First</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">View previous appointments.</h5>
        <p class="card-text">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Doloribus ex
          maxime est hic expedita vel assumenda at. Fuga, commodi placeat
          blanditiis nisi ex ut. Eaque possimus officia, illo perspiciatis quae
          reprehenderit aperiam ducimus ut. Ullam, atque vitae? Est odio nihil
          labore quo aliquid officia, voluptate rerum, quasi quam vel expedita!
        </p>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="card-header">Second</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">View Upcoming Appointments.</h5>
        <p class="card-text">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Non
          molestias excepturi laborum impedit dolorum quibusdam corporis quia
          nam voluptate, voluptatibus, laboriosam at blanditiis ad doloribus
          eligendi libero tempore deleniti deserunt! Explicabo aliquam officia
          sint error adipisci sequi molestiae nostrum voluptatum voluptate quam
          excepturi rem, praesentium eaque eos maxime dolorem dolore.
        </p>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer id="main-footer" class="bg-dark text-center pt-3">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mx-auto">
            <p class="text-white lead">
              All Rights Reserved, Copyright &copy; 2021
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"
      integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ZMP7rVo3mIykV+2+9J3UJ46jBk0WLaUAdn689aCwoqbBJiSnjAK/l8WvCWPIPm49"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-smHYKdLADwkXOn1EmN1qk/HfnUcbVRZyYmZ4qpPea6sjB/pTJ0euyQp0Mk8ck+5T"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
